{"type":"message","id":"e2f73f01","parentId":"23667012","timestamp":"2026-03-26T19:30:33.700Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"3A5B8186E0694DA38251\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"+573183718246\",\n  \"sender\": \"Gustavo Toledo\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Gustavo Toledo (+573183718246)\",\n  \"id\": \"+573183718246\",\n  \"name\": \"Gustavo Toledo\",\n  \"e164\": \"+573183718246\"\n}\n```\n\nY cual es el conflitto con el numero no pueden compartir la sesión?"}],"timestamp":1774553433694}}
