{"type":"message","id":"b88aa14b","parentId":"7dc9a66e","timestamp":"2026-03-26T19:48:28.389Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Listo Ares. Hoja creada en Notion dentro de `Atlas OS - Home`:\n\n**⚔️ Smart Project - Marcas del grupo**\n- Campos: Nombre, Ejercicio, Marca (kg), Reps, Series, Fecha, Notas\n- Ejercicios predefinidos: Press banca, Sentadilla, Peso muerto, Press militar, Dominadas, Otro\n\nCada vez que alguien del grupo reporte una marca, tú la registras directamente ahí. Flujo: grupo → Ares captura → Notion. Sin intermediarios."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":155,"cacheRead":115064,"cacheWrite":258,"totalTokens":115478,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774554502695,"responseId":"msg_0123pcp5UCQcj8jZHTcVZXkZ"}}
