{"type":"message","id":"bd220aa2","parentId":"f41c2f06","timestamp":"2026-03-27T01:13:02.648Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Lo veo claro: Ares no tiene `model` definido en `openclaw.json`, entonces hereda el default que es `openai-codex/gpt-5.4`. El 30B está en los modelos globales disponibles pero no asignado a Ares. Lo arreglo ahora:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_01GBccsHEZU9FjfpjCQXvfjm","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"$config = Get-Content \"C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\openclaw.json\" | ConvertFrom-Json\n\n# Agregar model a ares\n$aresIdx = ($config.agents.list | ForEach-Object { $i = 0 } { $i; $i++ } | Where-Object { $config.agents.list[$_].id -eq 'ares' })[0]\n\n$config.agents.list[$aresIdx] | Add-Member -MemberType NoteProperty -Name 'model' -Value ([PSCustomObject]@{\n  primary = 'ollama/qwen3:30b'\n  fallbacks = @('anthropic/claude-sonnet-4-6', 'openai-codex/gpt-5.4')\n}) -Force\n\n$config | ConvertTo-Json -Depth 20 | Out-File -Encoding utf8 -FilePath \"C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\openclaw.json\"\nWrite-Host \"OK - Ares model set to ollama/qwen3:30b\"","yieldMs":8000,"shell":"powershell"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":422,"cacheRead":103506,"cacheWrite":1012,"totalTokens":104941,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774573973125,"responseId":"msg_0182vPifYyeXAzEu9XkiToEz"}}
